24 “238A.125. (1) Upon retiring at normal retirement age, a vested pension
25 program member shall be paid an annual pension for the life of the member
26 as follows:
27 “(a) For service as a police officer or firefighter, 1.8 percent of final av-
28 erage salary multiplied by the number of years of retirement credit attrib-
29 utable to service as a police officer or firefighter.
30 “(b) For service as other than a police officer or firefighter, 1.5 percent
